casebody.data:
No. 09-9991. Donald Ray McCray, Petitioner v. Charlotte Booker. 560 U.S. 950, 130 S. Ct. 3394,

177 L. Ed. 2d 300,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4606. June 7, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Texas, Ninth District, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
